name: Starling
description: I think starlings are beautiful birds, black at a distance, but awash with a sheen of purples, greens, and glints of an iridescent nature. Starlings form huge murmurations at the seafront, but there are smaller groups of them here and there about the city. | 2592x3888px | f/9, 1/640s, 300mm | Canon 400D and Lightroom | Photographed 26th May 2021 just outside my house in Brighton, England
